channel.title: Ragersps - Brand new amazing 250+ custom server ready for players!
channel.description:
[size=12pt][size=10pt]ragersps.weebly.com is a dedicated 317 server With roughly over 250+ unique and custom rares awaiting to be dropped by countless arrays of npc's. Little to no down time, constant updating and fixing bugs tending to the communities desires. stats are level 1-125. very friendly staff, owner, and community members who are willing to have a conversation with anyone.[/size][/size]

A small insight as to what the server is all about and what you can do while enjoying your time online.
